WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Coach: Let’s make sure your destination is precise. What’s the 10X outcome?

2
00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:13.000
Client: We want to 10X qualified referrals in three years so we can run at stable utilization.

3
00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:18.000
Coach: What’s the single constraint that makes that hard right now?

4
00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:26.000
Client: We don’t have a COO and intake is fragmented. No one owns the referral engine.

5
00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:33.000
Coach: Great. What are the three 30-day commitments you’ll complete?

